last_episode_to_air.name: Dal Contadino, Ceviches by Divino & Jamerican Cuisine
last_episode_to_air.overview:
On this episode of Check, Please! South Florida, Michelle Bernstein and 3 guest reviewers explore South Florida cuisine, featuring Dal Contadino Trattoria in Fort Lauderdale, Ceviches By Divino in Miami Springs, and Jamerican Cuisine in Boynton Beach!

name: Check, Please! South Florida
overview: Check, Please! South Florida is a weekly, half-hour series hosted by chef Michelle Bernstein that gives amateur foodies the opportunity to review, rate and celebrate their favorite local restaurants.
